ck\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nio1665703006876.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nio1665703006876.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nio1665703006876.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nio1665703006876\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"nio1665703006876___clearselection_253872\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Built-in entity operation that clears the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$selected</span> attribute of\n      all occurrences of the entity.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"nio1665703006876__topic_d80831e1_d80832e1_d80833e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nio1665703006876__p_d80834e1_d80835e1_d80836e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$collhandle</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$clearselection()</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nio1665703006876__topic_d53242e1_d53243e1_d53244e1_d53245e1_d53246e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1218482e84\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nio1665703006876__p_d80840e1_d80841e1_d80842e1\">When an occurrence is selected, its built-in\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$selected</span> attribute is set to 1 and the occurrence is added to the\n            collection of selected occurrences. This attribute can be addressed using an occurrence\n            handle. For information, see the \"$occhandle\" and \"$selected\" topics.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nio1665703006876__p_d80843e1_d80844e1_d80845e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$collhandle</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$clearselection</span> to set the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$selected</span> attribute to\n            0 on all occurrences in the selected set.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fzs1718891991038.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occhandle</a><p>Returns the handle of the current occurrence of the specified entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xeq1665702701145.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$selected</a><p>Built-in occurrence attribute that indicates whether the occurrence is selected.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aco1665702561780.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Occurrences</a><p>An occurrence is the runtime instance of an entity. Although the entity determines the fields an occurrence may have, and some of its default properties and behavior, each occurrence is unique and contains one set of the fields, whether they contain data or not.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530271\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530271\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$clearselection Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Built-in entity operation that clears the $selected attribute of all occurrences of the entity. $collhandle { ( Entity ) } -> $clearselection() Description When an occurrence is selected, its built-in $selected attribute is set to 1 and the occurrence is added to the collection of selected occurrences. This attribute can be addressed using an occurrence handle. For information, see the \"$occhandle\" and \"$selected\" topics. You can use $collhandle -> $clearselection to set the $selected attribute to 0 on all occurrences in the selected set. Related Links $occhandle Returns the handle of the current occurrence of the specified entity. $selected Built-in occurrence attribute that indicates whether the occurrence is selected. Occurrences An occurrence is the runtime instance of an entity. Although the entity determines the fields an occurrence may have, and some of its default properties and behavior, each occurrence is unique and contains one set of the fields, whether they contain data or not. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}